passwordsafe: Password Safe is a password manager
passwordsafe: 
passwordsafe: It stores your passwords in an encrypted file, allowing
passwordsafe: you to remember only one password
passwordsafe: (the "master password"), instead of all the
passwordsafe: username/password combinations that you use.
passwordsafe: For extra security, you can use a Yubikey device to
passwordsafe: provide two-factor authentication.
passwordsafe: 
passwordsafe: Password Safe runs on Windows, Linux, macOS and FreeBSD.
